
Overview of noun contradiction

The noun contradiction has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                  
1. (7) contradiction -- (opposition between two conflicting forces or ideas)
2. (1) contradiction, contradiction in terms -- ((logic) a statement that is necessarily false; "the statement `he is brave and he is not brave' is a contradiction")
3. contradiction -- (the speech act of contradicting someone; "he spoke as if he thought his claims were immune to contradiction")
